    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="4bba5-102"><xref:System.Convert.ToBase64CharArray%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>和<xref:System.Convert.ToBase64String%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>方法的 8 位元不帶正負號整數的陣列值轉換為 base 64 數字所組成的相等字串表示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4bba5-102">The <xref:System.Convert.ToBase64CharArray%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> and <xref:System.Convert.ToBase64String%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> methods convert the value of an array of 8-bit unsigned integers to an equivalent string representation that consists of base 64 digits.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4bba5-103">字串表示可以包含一或多個換行，其中換行符號定義為歸位字元傳回字元 (U + 000 D)，後面接著換行字元 (U + 000A)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4bba5-103">The string representation can contain one or more line breaks, where a line break is defined as a carriage return character (U+000D) followed by a line feed character (U+000A).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4bba5-104">換行符號會被視為在 base-64 編碼的空格字元，因為它們時，會忽略轉換 base-64 編碼字串的位元組陣列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4bba5-104">Because line breaks are considered white-space characters in a base-64 encoding, they are ignored when converting a base-64 encoded string back to a byte array.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4bba5-105">控制項或裝置，例如主控台視窗中顯示的已編碼的字串時，會只是方便的分行符號。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4bba5-105">The line breaks are simply convenient when displaying the encoded string to a control or a device such as a console window.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="4bba5-106">None 和 InsertLineBreaks 值都會互斥。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4bba5-106">The None and InsertLineBreaks values are mutually exclusive.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4bba5-107">因此，雖然<xref:System.Base64FormattingOptions.None?displayProperty=nameWithType>列舉型別會標示<xref:System.FlagsAttribute>屬性，並沒有任何意義來執行這兩個值的位元組合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4bba5-107">Therefore, although the <xref:System.Base64FormattingOptions.None?displayProperty=nameWithType> enumeration is marked with the <xref:System.FlagsAttribute> attribute, it makes no sense to perform a bitwise combination of these two values.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="4bba5-108">下列範例會呼叫<xref:System.Convert.ToBase64String%28System.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.Base64FormattingOptions%29?displayProperty=nameWithType>InsertLineBreaks 插入列的引數將會編碼所產生的 100 個元素的位元組陣列的字串中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4bba5-108">The following example calls the <xref:System.Convert.ToBase64String%28System.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.Base64FormattingOptions%29?displayProperty=nameWithType> with a InsertLineBreaks argument to insert line breaks in the string that is produced by encoding a 100-element byte array.</span></span>  
  
