 <span data-ttu-id="4bba5-109">做為範例所示，從輸出<xref:System.Convert.FromBase64String%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>成功還原原始的位元組陣列; 分行符號字元會在轉換期間忽略。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4bba5-109">As the output from the example shows, the <xref:System.Convert.FromBase64String%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> succeeds in restoring the original byte array; the line break characters are ignored during the conversion.</span></span>  
  
